  <entry>
    <title>好像真的好起来了</title>
    <link href="https://ashburshui.github.io/2025/03/06/humble/%E5%A5%BD%E5%83%8F%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86/"/>
    <id>https://ashburshui.github.io/2025/03/06/humble/%E5%A5%BD%E5%83%8F%E7%9C%9F%E7%9A%84%E5%A5%BD%E8%B5%B7%E6%9D%A5%E4%BA%86/</id>
    <published>2025-03-06T16:00:00.000Z</published>
    <updated>2025-03-11T19:24:07.751Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote><p>哈哈，😂好不容易，珍惜机会，巩固好习惯，能感到自信真的回来了。<br><span id="more"></span></p></blockquote><p><img src="/blog-images/earthrise.jpg" alt=""></p><p>和另一个<a href="https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E6%9A%97%E6%B7%A1%E8%97%8D%E9%BB%9E">link</a></p><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone -1:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">What a unknown battle...!!! I always love the messy stuff... 记得这天。。。临在中没了emo</span><br><span class="line">大大方方，思路和表达清晰 - show up, say Hi, get the work done</span><br><span class="line">I.Goals II.Focus(pinch the brain) III.对事情的理解 - 猴子，果汁，多巴胺，想明白了沒？合理起伏，柔性，灰度的视角，😂停下来享受享受，慢慢来</span><br><span class="line">Mindful，不麻木，重视early red sign，take actions immediately，不然压力会逐渐积累，最后把自己压垮啦，学会navigate，脸皮超级厚...</span><br><span class="line">问题简单的原因：实事求是，抓住了要害，愿赌服输，不要怨天尤人</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone 0:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">心理健康，和睦友爱（理智的家庭），都是人嘛，能理解和共情，有爱的能力，错误的教育，或者观念，把人憋得难受，而不是具体的事物。</span><br><span class="line">恐惧，焦虑，神经症的背后是什么？想明白了，其实是情感和认知的发展过程，&quot;trauma resolution process&quot;。</span><br><span class="line">只能行动，直面和享受恐惧与困难，链接更好的关系，别无他法，大大方方做健康的自己。</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone 1:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">* 想明白什么是胡说八道，和高明的💉</span><br><span class="line">+ 定位到问题了，就不可怕，慢慢处理1)压力反应问题 &amp; 2)社会交往。</span><br><span class="line">不要自责，往前走就行了，1)都荒唐过 &amp; 2)往往最关键的选择，就是在年轻的时候，见识不足的时候做出的</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Milestone 2:</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">把该做的事情，按时保质保量做好，离开一个节点时，不后悔</span><br><span class="line">继续做 &quot;+&quot; in mildstone 1 card</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
    <summary type="html">&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;哈哈，😂好不容易，珍惜机会，巩固好习惯，能感到自信真的回来了。&lt;br&gt;</summary>
    
    
    
    
